content.text:
Where am I?  What a strange land!  
Maybe I should talk to the Wizard over there to find out what is going on!

parameters:
"Hello adventurer! You must travel to the East to meet with the King.
I will meet you there. (Press space to clear this message)"
"Some type of barrier is blocking my way."
"You hear the sound of crumbling walls..."
"These snowballs are freezing me to death! I need to find some protection to get past them. You hear the wizard in your mind... 'Let me help you escape."

"Hello again. You will need to speak with the King to begin your quest. 
You will need to find the snow amulet to porve your worth. 
Use the signs to help you find your way. Return here when you have it."

"Excellent, you have the amulet! 
You are now ready to cross the sea and meet with the King. 
You have finished the Mini Adventure."
